204
00:14:45,175 --> 00:14:48,971
We must do something while you're in here,
and while I'm outside.

205
00:14:50,097 --> 00:14:52,766
We just failed. We didn't give up.

206
00:15:00,608 --> 00:15:03,736
I do not want to give up
on the mine case either.

207
00:15:04,361 --> 00:15:06,655
Plus, I made a promise to you too.

208
00:15:06,739 --> 00:15:09,158
You said you'll end it in 90 days,
didn't you?

209
00:15:09,241 --> 00:15:10,117
I did.

210
00:15:10,743 --> 00:15:12,161
I cannot take three months off.

211
00:15:12,828 --> 00:15:14,538
I must wrap up the mine case.

212
00:15:15,372 --> 00:15:18,208
Both of us are excluded from duty.

213
00:15:18,292 --> 00:15:20,336
We cannot do anything officially.

214
00:15:20,419 --> 00:15:22,671
Affairs of the world
and case investigations

215
00:15:23,172 --> 00:15:25,299
aren't always done officially.

216
00:15:25,382 --> 00:15:27,718
And I don't take
the path someone tells me to take.

217
00:15:28,427 --> 00:15:29,595
Don't you know how I am?

218
00:15:32,598 --> 00:15:33,766
Call me.

219
